OL,5,Csentence
OL,7,FAndrew Bone, from Sale, sent out a
OL,8,Fvile tweet on 11 July 2021 directed at
OL,9,Fpenalty takers Bukayo Saka, Jadon
OL,10,FSancho and Marcus Rashford. England
OL,11,Fdid not win the shoot out against
OL,12,FItaly.
OL,14,FBone deleted the post and tried to
OL,15,Fclaim he had been hacked, but it had
OL,16,Falready been retweeted and was
OL,17,Freported to both his employer - who
OL,18,Flater sacked him - and the authorities.
