OL,5,Csentence
OL,7,FPolice arrested Bone three days after
OL,8,Fthe final and used mobile phone mast
OL,9,Fanalysis to prove he had sent the
OL,10,Ftweet. Officers also found hateful
OL,11,Fcomments he had previously made on
OL,12,Fsocial media.
OL,14,FIn court, the 41-year-old initially
OL,15,Fdenied the charge before changing his
OL,16,Fplea. He wept in the dock as he was
OL,17,Fgiven a six-week prison sentence,
OL,18,Fsuspended for 12 months.
