OL,5,Csentence
OL,7,FSenior Crown Prosecutor Martin Brogan
OL,8,Fsaid: "Andrew Bone took to social
OL,9,Fmedia to post a hateful racist
OL,10,Fcomment, and in doing so, he broke the
OL,11,Flaw.
OL,13,F"We want supporters to show their
OL,14,Fpassion without crossing the line into
OL,15,Fcriminality.
