OL,5,Csentence
OL,7,F"Hateful and offensive comments around
OL,8,Four national sport cause a great deal
OL,9,Fof distress and we stand ready to
OL,10,Fprosecute whenever so-called fans use
OL,11,Fracist, hateful or otherwise offensive
OL,12,Fcomments, both in person and online."
OL,14,FFootball anti-racism campaign group
OL,15,FKick It Out have questioned whether
OL,16,FBone's sentence is enough of a
OL,17,Fdeterrent.
