OL,5,Csentence
OL,7,FTheir CEO, Samuel Okafor, told ITV
OL,8,FNews: "We want to be able to send a
OL,9,Fmessage to those individuals who feel
OL,10,Fthat they can post discriminatory
OL,11,Fmessages on social media.
OL,13,F"I'm not sure that the timescale it's
OL,14,Ftaken to reach a decision here, but
OL,15,Falso the length of the consequence...
OL,16,Freally sends a message out there."
